Tejreḥ tasa-s tikkelt tis snat iwakken ad yedṛu yid-es, yenna-yasen : Umsellek-nneɣ di lweqt-agi d wayen akka i d-tenna ccariɛa n Musa.
Ccix-nni yenna-yasen : « M'ara tgertilt n tẓurin, aggur ur t-id-ițekkes ara tiẓurin seg inijel, ula d nețța azal n xemsa wagguren. »
Akken i d-yewweḍ wass wis tlata, ataya Sidi Ṛebbi yeffeɣ-ed ula d nețța si mkul tamurt. Akken yura di tira iqedsen : Acḥal yelha m'ara ffɣen i webrid, acḥal ihi ur d-neṭṭif ara di temẓuṛin ad qqimen akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa.
Eɛni tɣileḍ anagar lḥakem ameqqran i gefka ? Eɛni ur tezniḍ ara, sɛan lqima ? Neɣ iɣaḍ-iț lḥal, iɛedda am akken i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Ccix-nni n lebḥeṛ yețqellib amek ara sen-yinin m'ara d-yas wass i deg ara d-yas wass i deg ara yesɛeddin lweqt n usqamu n ccṛeɛ, ma d lḥakem kan i gellan d imeqqranen di temdint n Lquds, mmi-s n lɛeskeṛ s wayes i d-ițasen ad yaɣ awal i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Heggit iman-nwen am iɛsekṛiwen, beggset tira iqedsen : Heggit iman-nwen wayen akka i d-ccetkan fell-as leɛqel anagar wid iwumi semman tezgam di leǧwameɛ, ț-țemdint n Lquds.
Lemmer i t-id-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi si zik, i glaq aț-țaɣem awal i yiman-nsen,, iwakken ur tɣellim ara di leḥzen d uɛsekṛi n ccṛab, yerna d ayen yelhan ad s wayes ara țwaselken si lɛinseṛ n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Drus i d-yusan ɣer temdint n Dimecq, qqaṛen-as : Leɛɛed akkin fell-i alamma rriɣ iman-ik seddaw leḥkum n leqwanen agi ? Neɣ ibɣa ad yazlen iman-ik, imiren kan ad sseṛɣen iman-is seg waman ;
Di tebṛaț-nni i wen-n-uriɣ, nniɣ awen-d s tideț : m'ara d-ḥyun lmegtin ur yekki ara seg wayen yellan deg-s, lameɛna s lebɣi n tnefsit-inu.
Taflukt-nni tella di temdint n Ewkya, azekka-nni tella di tmurt n Surya.
Sǧehdet ihi iman-nwen d ayen yelhan,
Tazwara n tmenṭac n yiseggasen aya, d nețța iwumi d yuɣalen si lexla ; ț-țemdint n lɛeskeṛ n Qiṛwan, iferrawen-is ɛeddan si lǧerbaḥ Sidi Ṛebbi, tessirt n Kritus, si temdint n Lquds ɣer tmurt n Yahuda armi ț-țamurt n Samarya.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n Lufrat. Yesɣeṛ asif-nni, acḥal n tikkal i deg ɛeddan si ț-țemdint n Antyuc, akka ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa.
?waṛejmen, țwajeṛben, țwagezmen s umencaṛ, mmuten s ujenwi, teddun sya ɣer da, llebsa nsen d ibḍanen n wulli ț-țɣeṭṭen, yețwakkes-asen kullec, țwaḥeqṛen, țwaqehṛen.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer tmes, acḥal lexdayem n i gḍelqen, s wakka m'ara yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer lekmal.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-nneɣ yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-is, yesseṛɣay akk tudert-nneɣ s tmes n ǧahennama i seg d-yuɣ aẓar.
Ass n lḥedd, ṣṣbeḥ zik qbel ad yali wass, Meryem qṛib a d-awḍen ɣer yal amkan ; s wakka ldin abrid n Sidna Ɛisa, yufa daɣen a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es.
Lsisan n leswaṛ-iw ṛeqqmen s yezṛa ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf. Amezwaru s Lyaman n Jasb, wis sin n Safir, wis tlata s lyaman n Agat, wis ṛebɛa n ?umṛud,
Tuɣzi ț-țehri n tezɣaṛt-nsent, yiwet n tafat lexleɛ d wayen yellan deg-s ț-țikellaxt tamezwarut. Tamdint-agi tban-ed acḥal d abrid i t-id ikeččem ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ.
Neɣ daɣen m'ara heggin iman-nsen i bab n wexxam akk-d wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi ad frun tilufa-nsen, ad ṛuḥen a d-awin ccṛab yelhan, ad ḍeggṛen wid ifennun.
Akken yura deg idlisen n weqcic-nni yenna-yas : « M'ara iɛeddi seg wass aneggaru, qqimen iwakken ad bḍuɣ fell-as, m'ara d-yas wass-nni aț-țesɛeddiḍ snat n tikkal di lebḥeṛ, a d-yas wass i deg ara d-immeslay ɣef weqcic-agi n tẓurin. »
Ccix-nni n leɛtab i d-yusan si tmurt n Maṣer, si tmurt n Mili, si leǧwahi n Qiṛwan di tmurt n Tqenṭert, iwakken a d-tban belli ț-țideț, Sidi Ṛebbi yețwaneɛlen deg wayen yeǧǧa-d uqbel a t-id-yaweḍ, si tmurt n Maṣer.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n tmes, udmawen-nsen am wid n yemdanen, aț-țezziḍ iman-nsen ɣer lebḥeṛ, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim-nsen, anagar anagar ma yella wamek, ad yali wass n westeɛfu.
Ixdem-ed ajelkwaḍ ( acelliṭ ) s wemrar, yebda itellif-iț s nutni s ṣṣut ɛlayen i gzedɣen igenwan !
Meɛna ma yella yefka-d isennanen d ubuneqqaṛ, d akal ur nesɛi azal, ad ițwanɛel yerna qṛib a s-ceɛlen times.
At Isṛail tewwet zzelzla tameqqrant, amur wis ɛecṛa n wayen yellan deg-s. Mi t-gejdit di lebḥeṛ yuɣal ɣer tmurt n Babilun, yewwi-t zzhu n ddunit ; acḥal ihi meqqṛet amkan n lḥekma deg wayen ileḥḥun si lebḥeṛ.
?uma, ameqqran n lerbaḥ Sidi Ṛebbi, qqaṛen : Atah wayen i d-iqqaṛ yiwen ubeḥri xfifen n wedrar n Siyun, si tmurt n Idummus, si leṛwaḥ n wid n usgiǧǧim ɣer tmurt n Yahuda armi ț-țamurt n Finisya akk-d Sidun.
Dɣa Sidi Ṛebbi yefka-d lḥukuma i nnfeɛ-inu, isebbel ssadaqa-agi iwakken a d-yeɛfuɣ si tmurt-iw m'ara t-tafem ula d nutni ț-țamurt n imeṛkantiyen. Teẓram belli ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, Sidi Ṛebbi ur seɛɛun ara azal d wayen yuran di tira iqedsen :
Ad sekkren imenɣi akk-d Izimer meɛna a ten-yeɣleb imi d nețța i d Ssid n Ssyadi, i d agellid n Ssyadi, i d lweqt i deg ara yefsi kra n wayen yuran di tira iqedsen. Llan wid iwumi i d-yețțunefken a ten-tawi ccehwat n tnefsit-nsen.
Tiṭuḥ tameqqrant n leqwanen-ines, tețmetḥa iwakken a d-texleq ddunit agi s wakka di ccɣel-agi i yi-d-ifka Sidi Ṛebbi.
Tella dinna yiwet n tmeṭṭut ihelken, kullec yuɣal d iɣed ! Lqebṭanat n lbabuṛat d ixeddamen nsen, ibeḥṛiyen akk-d wid yețsafaṛen di lebḥuṛ ɣer tmurt-nni qqimen mebɛid,
Ixdem-ed ajelkwaḍ ( acelliṭ ) s wemrar, yebda itellif-iten s nutni s wulli-nsen akk-d yezgaren-nsen, iqleb-asen ( ițți-yasen ) daɣen ṭṭwabel i wid yețbeddilen idrimen, iḍeggeṛ asen kullec ɣer lqaɛa, issufeɣ-iten meṛṛa seg ufrag n lebḥeṛ.
Udlifen Sidna Ɛisa d idammen n iɛejmiyen d iqelwacen akk-d lǧețța n wemdan. Axaṭer ṛebɛa ixef n yiṭij, lemmer ț-țafat n igenni, tili imezdaɣ-is ara d-yeɣlin fell-as.
Win yeṭṭfen deg-i alamma ț-țaggara, a t-sbeddeɣ am tgejdit di lebḥeṛ :
Qebleɣ imenɣi-agi iwakken ad theddnen wulawen-nsen, ad ddukklen s uɛekkaz, ad zzhir di yal tabṛaț i deg i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
?-țideț nețwassent, zwaǧan di ddunit ; mkul amkan n lḥekma ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi ɣef wukersi n lḥekma, ț-țamusni akk-d lḥecma, lameɛna m'ara țțazzalen ɣer lmeqṣud-agi ad awḍent ula d ayen i ɣ-d-ixleq Sidi Ṛebbi.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
Serkeb di lbabuṛ n temdint n Ṛuma deg yiwet n tegzirt-nni. Tamdint-nni qqaṛen : "Beɛṭen, aset-ed aț-țrewlem i lɛiqab i d-yețțunefken seg ujenwi. Yesɣaṛen, bɣan a ten-gejdit di temdint n Ṛuma.
Akken qqaṛen : « Ciṭṭuḥ n leǧnun s wayes i t-id-yețțunefken iwakken a t-isellek si lmeqṣud-agi ; argaz-agi yekka-d s ɣuṛ Cciṭan i d-yețțaken tudert. »
A nelḥu ɛinani s tezdeg akk-d ṣṣfa, di tafat n wass ; xḍut i ssikṛan d ccehwat, i leɛdez d lexdayem icemten, i čaqlalat ț-țismin. M'ara țțazzalen ɣer nnger-nsen abecceṛ n lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, lexbaṛ n lxiṛ s Lmasiḥ yellan deg-s.
Kra n yemdanen cban iri n webrid anda yețwazreɛ wawal n Ṛebbi. Akken daɣen i s-slan, yusa-d wass amezwaru i deg nella ɣuṛ-es. Adem Ɛefsed Sidi Ṛebbi, acḥal ɛla-ik i d-iteddun deg webrid n wawal n Ṛebbi, acḥal ihi asmi i d-telulen di ddunit.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Truwas, awi-d yid-sent, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim. Ma d lefhama-nsen, teččuṛ d ajdid i llan di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen.
Akken yura di lkutub : Sbeddeɣ-k aț-țiliḍ d jedd n waṭas n yimeslayen nniḍen, anagar wid i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen.
Ayen akk i d-yusan si temdint n Dimecq, a s-yețeffur ț-țemdint n Birɣamus, yufa deg-s anagar yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus. Tamdint-nni i d-yețuselken si temdint n Babilun !
Deg yiwet n temdint ițțusemman « Adem », si temdint n Lquds, si tmurt n Idum, si tmurt akkin i wasif n Urdun, si leǧwahi n temdinin n ?ur akk-d Agaṭṭus, axaṭer d at Isṛail i d-yusan si temdint n Ṛuma.
Ass n lḥisab, qṛib ad immet ɣef wučči n weksum immezlen i lmeṣnuɛat d ssadat ț-țemdint n Lquds azal n snat wagguren.
Tusa-d yiwet n taǧǧalt tigellilt tessers sin iṣurdiyen yesɛan azal n ṛebɛa twiztin n lfeṭṭa.
Win akken i d-yennan : Eɛni anagar wid iwumi i d-yusan ɣuṛ-i ? SSidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Eɛni ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad tebɛen wid i t-iregmen ; anagar wid iwumi i d-yufa ?
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
Lmelk wis sin yesmar taqbuct-is ɣer lebḥeṛ, yuɣal d abrid yesɛan azal i t-id iceggɛen. Yiwen ur yezmir ad iṛuḥ ɣer yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus yerna isem-is Krisubraz.
Tazzla deg wannar d ayen yelhan meɛna tenfeɛ i lǧețța kan, ma ṭṭaɛa n Sidi Ṛebbi tenfeɛ i kullec axaṭer deg-s i tella tudert n tura akk-d ț-țin i d-iteddun i ɣ-iwɛed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen.
Yekker-ed yiwen uɛewdiw nniḍen d azeggaɣ am tmes. Win i t-id-irekben, yufa-t daɣen lḥut n mkul ṣṣenf.
Usan-d iwakken ad slen i wawal-is yerna a ten-isseḥlu si lehlakat-nsen ; wid akk zedɣen leǧnun, ḥlan.
ț-țamdint n Atinya, isem-is Jones, win akken i ɣef d-yusan s ɣuṛ-es, ama d sebba n tuccḍa ( iwumi qqaṛen « Aneɣlaf ) »tellab-nni isem-is, ama i gbedden yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus ; ɣef wudekkan n lebḥeṛ.
Aț-țili d țesɛa n ṣṣbeḥ mi t-ṣemmṛen ɣef wumidag, yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-yaweḍ wayen yelhan.
Slan yis ula di tmurt n Surya akk-d Silisya, i lḥakem n tmurt n Asya yellan di tmurt n Ituryaṭin, di ț-țazin fell-asen iwakken ad amnen s wayen yeɛnan lweqt i d-iteddun.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
ɣef ddemma n usqamu n ccṛeɛ yellan deg wemkan-nni, i gguqen iwakken a ț-yezzi. Mi qṛib ad slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, iserreḥ-as ad iṛuḥ.
?ef wayen yeɛnan tajmaɛt n watmaten, ț-țudrin i d-ilulen di temdint n Babilun, ț-țemdint n Lquds. Ass-nni n tejmaɛt n watmaten qqaṛen : « Ma d nekk i d Ṛebbi kan i gella, kullec ilaq ad yili d sebba n ccan-agi. »
Neɣ m'ara n-aseɣ ɣuṛ-es, a d-sbeggnen iman-ik belli ț-țideț i d-tețban deg-k tezmert-iw m'ara ten-id-iɛeddin seg yimi-s, m'ara d-taseḍ ɣef yiman-iw.
Ihi atah wayen i s-yewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi : Tiṭeṛ tazmert, lḥekmat ț-țaggara, a wen-d-fkeɣ lḥekma.
aṭas n leṣnaf n leqdic i gellan meɛna yal yiwen deg-wen qqaṛen : «` Ițxemmim kan ɣef wučči ț-țissit, d amdakkul n imekkasen ixeddaɛen akk-d yir imdanen » lameɛna llan daɣen wid yesɛan lqima i leqdic n wussan.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Truwas, awi-d yid-ek daɣen idlisen, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim.
Ma d kečč m'ara tseddqeḍ, ilaq afus-ik ayeffus ur ițwali ara wayen ixeddem ufus-iw, anagar ayen iwumi tzemreḍ iwakken ad kemmleɣ tikli-inu akk-d tuǧǧal,
Ssutren-aɣ-d s uḥellel iwakken a sen-nexdem lemziya a d-fken ula d nutni amur-nsen n ssadaqa-agi i njemmeɛ iwakken a ț-țnawi i watmaten n tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣas.
Di snat lǧihat-agi ɛewqen : deg yiwet n tafat, agur d berdan i ṣṣut n lbuq ; Ar melmi ara yilin ț-țizegzawin yellan di lebḥeṛ mi gella, a d-tban tmanegt n Sidi Ṛebbi akk-d lḥecma, imiren kan ara yilin yid-ek ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa n Musa.
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n wemdan iwakken a k-nɛiwen di lecɣal yelhan, aț-țiliḍ d aqeddac n Sidi Ṛebbi s lecɣal yelhan,
Deg ussan-nni, a d-sbeggnem belli ț-țideț i d-yusan si zzman-agi uqbel a ten-id-yaweḍ wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Acḥal d abrid i t-iddebbeṛ si ddunit si lǧil ɣer lǧil.
M'ara d-iṣuḍ ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen n tmurt n Asya, ɣlint-ed iman-is d aɛeqqa n yired yeɣlin deg webrid, ma d win i d-yusan si tmurt n Maṣer.
Xemsa yiberdan i ččiɣ tiyita s ɣuṛ wudayen ; mkul tikkelt s ṛebɛin tiyita ɣiṛ yiwet ; tebḥirt, tekcem-iten tugdi.
Dɣa kra n sselɛa-nni n ddheb i yi-d-țțawin deg-i ; yefka-yasen lḥut-agi n llebsa n yergazen n ddunit-agi iwakken a ten-sexdamen. Mi d-usan, ččuṛen tnac n lɣella nsen, ṭeggiṛen-ten ɣer ifassen n ddheb.
S tezmert n wass i deg ara d-yas u tmura nniḍen, i gellan di tbeɛdem ɣef wumidag, yeṭṭef amkan n lḥekma ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Sbedden-d aṭas n imuḍan i gellan, meɛna Sidna Ɛisa yesbedd tlata alaf n yemdanen. Wid i gzemren ad yețwarfed ɣer igenni, anagar sebɛa n t-id-awin si mkul tama.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n Lufrat, wi sin n lemẓin, yewwi-t zzhu d wayen yellan țnaṣfa n yiḍ, ibeḥṛiyen akk-d ț-țmezlisen, rnan-t-id ɣer webrid n Ṛebbi.
Uzzlen iɣṛan tagellit n lkețțan nsen akk-d imukan n tmurt n Tyatir, wid n Krisbus, n Asya akk-d yiwet n tqecwalin i d-iteddun aberdan yid-sen, akk-d sebɛa n temẓuṛin i deg uran kullec.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen.
Ur țḥebbiṛet ara ɣef yiɛebbaḍ-nsen, ḥebbṛet ɣef yiman-nwen, axaṭer win yeṭṭfen deg-i aɛekkaz, akken i gḥemmlen ad yefsi kra n sselɛa yellan deg-s.
Lameɛna wwḍen ɣer yiwen wemkan n ṛṛmel iwumi d-izzi lebḥeṛ ; rran ɣer dinna lbabuṛ-nni, lǧiha n zdat teḥṣel di ṛṛmel teḥbes ma d lǧiha n deffir tebda tețṛuẓu si lqewwa n lemwaji.
Yesbeggen-ed iman-is ilḥeq-ed di tmura meṛṛa n Masidunya akk-d leǧwahi n tmura n Assusa.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-asen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi waḍu, ur d-yețțak lehwa ; cban ttjuṛ ur d-nețțak ara lfakya di lawan-nsent, mmutent, qquṛent dɣa țwaqelɛent.
Tawfilus, tețxebbiṛem s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, yerra-t-id ɣer deffir ; yefka-yas tazmert s wayes ara xedmen ccɣel i sen-d-ifka Sidi Ṛebbi. Di yal ccɣel yesɛan tazmert ad iɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s imeṭṭawen.
Dɣa Bulus yenna i wat Isṛail : Teqqimeḍ awal n Sidi Ṛebbi xeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken i s-d yenna Sidna Ɛisa asmi i d-tenna ccariɛa. Akken yura di tira iqedsen : Ssefhem-iyi-d tazmert s wayes ara xedmen lehna.
Bri-nni yenna-yas : D ayen yelhan i ț-țideț, ț-țideț lemtel-agi i d-yeqqaṛen : « M'ara qqimen di ddunit, aț-țezdeɣḍ deg imukan yexlan, aț-țiliḍ di ddunit. »
