Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tzemmurt n lɛali ɣas akken d aḥeccad i telliḍ, acḥal ihi i k-ishel i nutni yellan ț-țiṣeḍwa n tzemmurt iwakken ad uɣalen ad țțuleqmen ɣef tzemmurt-nsen.
A d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lewḥuc : ama d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, ama d ifṛax, ama d izerman ama d lewḥuc n lebḥeṛ yerna ț-țideț iɣleb-iten meṛṛa.
Ɣef ddemma n yimeslayen-agi, ffɣen si temdint n ?udum, kra n yemdanen mazal-iten ddren ar tura, kra deg-sen mmuten.
Deg ul-is i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi-s, qṛib a d-nefken i laẓ d fad, meɛna ula d ccbaḥa-ines a d-yeǧǧ deffir-sen.
Leḥjab yellan deg umkan iqedsen di lǧameɛ, icerreg ɣef sin seg yixef ufella, armi d ixef n wadda. Lqaɛa tergagi, idurar ceqqeqen,
Deg ussan-nni, a d-sbeggil lexbaṛ-agi n lxiṛ i wen-d-nniɣ « Dawed », anagar kra n win yellan d sebba n tuccḍa, di leqdic-nsen ur nesɛi lmeɛna.
Di temdint n Ikunyum, ufan-t-id yiwen n wesɣaṛ d wamek i ten-id-yețwaxedmen s tmeslayt-nsen : "Ma ț-țudrin, a d-tban belli ț-țamdint n Kritus i d-ițfeggiḍen seg yimi-s.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Leḥjab n wemkan iqedsen n lǧameɛ, icerreg ɣef sin seg yixef ufella, armi d ixef n wadda.
Walit daɣen lbabuṛ, ɣas d ameqqran, yețsuḍu deg-s waḍu iǧehden, meɛna s yiwen ujeggu d ameẓyan, lqebṭan-ines issedduy-it ɣer wanda yebɣa.
A d-yas umɛellem-iw m'ara yeṛsan, ad yili di tɛebbuṭ n yemma-s, ad yazzin deg uxxam alamma ț-țaggara n leɛtab ameqqran, aț-țiliḍ ț-țamecṭuḥt di lebḥeṛ.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Sudum d Gumuṛ akk-d tudrin i sent-id-yezzin, ixeddmen anagar ticmatin d zzna, qqiment-ed d lemtel mi tent-yessenger Sidi Ṛebbi s tmes yecban times n ǧahennama ;
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen. LLlan daɣen wid iḥeṛmen iman-nsen ɣef zwaǧ, ɣef ddemma n lexṛif.
